name: Deconstruction - grain
description:
Archaic elements, fire and serendipity, simultaneously decompose and reconstitute. Generative random generation overlaps with existing and gives rise to new.

Deconstruction began as a series of iterative designs that sought to capture graphic layers and densities through exploratory experimentation.
 
- Deconstruction - soft
- Experimental Deconstruction
- Created with digital-analogue mixed media
